Please submit bug reports at:
http://mangos.lighthouseapp.com/

Discussion mailing list:
http://groups.google.com/group/mangos-core

Version 0.6.0.01
* The authentication and realm list server has been rewritten. It now is feature
  complete, and supports full account and realm management, and allows client
  connections from World of Warcraft client version 3.0.2 build 9056 in any
  client language.
* The authentication and realm list server now features full account management.
  This includes support for complete account data including address, payment
  information, subscriptions, parental control, expansion support using custom
  expansion keys.

Version 0.5.0.02
* MaNGOS2 has received a lot of love, and allows client connections from World
  of Warcraft client version 1.2.1 build 4150 up to client version 1.4.0 build
  4341 in any client language.

Version 0.5.0.01
* Initial release of MaNGOS2, now following the principles of Agile Software
  development.
